COMMENTS
--------
To me,this is the most entertaining movie of 2013,like Bhooter Bhobisyot it also has rhythimic dialogues but not excesive and importantly social message in the form of comedy, well supported with powerful performance of actors.
Who can forget the twist at the end! That is the speciality of this movie and Anik Dutta himself. Though the original writing of Shirshendu was directed towards the children mainly,but Anik gracefully moved the direction from children to adults starting from the begining. :)
